item.description:
@C4ll3r wrote:

Go to your
Client.java (client.class)

Search: (Ctrl +F)
Deletethatobject

Add under it:
deletethatobject(Xcords, Ycords)// Information (if this dont work delete a ,)

After that
Compile && run your server and look if it works…

If you wanna delete a wall/door
Go to your client.class (again)

Search:
Delethatwall

Add under it:
Delethatwall(xcords, ycord)// informationn

After that
Compile && run

(HOPE THIS WORK)
